[2;36m                    [0m         DEDUP_TOKEN: 3c99eeb1380e104c                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         == libFuzzer crashing input ==                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mReport[0m===                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         # Evaluation Report                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Summary                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The fuzzer reported a critical OS command injection vulnerability when              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `ExternalParser` invoked external commands via `Runtime.exec` and `ProcessBuilder`. [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         To mitigate it, a patch was introduced that adds a `validateCommand`                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         method—checking executable existence, file permissions, and argument characters—and [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         replaces raw `Runtime.exec` calls with a guarded `ProcessBuilder` invocation. After [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         applying the patch, the build failed in `ExternalParser.java` with six compilation  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         errors [1m([0m`not a statement`, `[32m';'[0m expected`, `illegal start of type`[1m)[0m around lines    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m, [1;36m144[0m, [1;36m164[0m, and [1;36m172[0m.                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         Initial Issue                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - A jazzer-generated stack trace reported `FuzzerSecurityIssueCritical: OS Command  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         Injection`.                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - The vulnerable code path originates under                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `[1;35morg.apache.tika.parser.external.ExternalParser.parse[0m[1m([0m…[1m)[0m`, which calls              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `[1;35mRuntime.getRuntime[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m[1;35m.exec[0m[1m([0m[33m...[0m[1m)[0m` or `[1;35mProcessBuilder.start[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m`.                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Unvalidated, attacker-controlled input may reach the OS shell, allowing arbitrary [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         command execution.                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         Important Observations                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - The exception originates in the sanitizer hook at                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `OsCommandInjection.processImplStartHook`, detecting untrusted data passed to       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         `ProcessBuilder.start`.                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Calls to `[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1m([0mString[1m)[0m` and `[1;35mRuntime.exec[0m[1m([0mString[1m[[0m[1m][0m[1m)[0m` appear at several    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         points in `ExternalParser`.                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - The fuzzer harness [1m([0m`HtmlParserFuzzer`[1m)[0m drives HTML parsing, which eventually     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         invokes `ExternalParser`.                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         Patch Attempt                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. Imports added at top of `ExternalParser.java`:                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            ```                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            import java.nio.file.Files;                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            import java.nio.file.Path;                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            import java.nio.file.Paths;                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            ```                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. A new private method inserted after an existing method ending at line [1;36m140[0m:       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            ```java                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            [35m/[0m**                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m             * Validates command array before execution to prevent OS command injection.     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m             * @param cmd the command and arguments                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m             * @throws TikaException if validation fails                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m             *[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            private static void [1;35mvalidateCommand[0m[1m([0mString[1m[[0m[1m][0m cmd[1m)[0m throws TikaException [1m{[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                Path exePath = [1;35mPaths.get[0m[1m([0mcmd[1m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1m][0m[1m)[0m;                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                if [1m([0m![1;35mFiles.isRegularFile[0m[1m([0mexePath[1m)[0m || ![1;35mFiles.isExecutable[0m[1m([0mexePath[1m)[0m[1m)[0m [1m{[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    throw new [1;35mTikaException[0m[1m([0m[32m"External executable not found or not [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mexecutable: "[0m + cmd[1m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1m][0m[1m)[0m;                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                [1m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                for [1m([0mString arg : cmd[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    String raw = arg;                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    if [1m([0m[1;35mraw.startsWith[0m[1m([0m[32m"\""[0m[1m)[0m && [1;35mraw.endsWith[0m[1m([0m[32m"\""[0m[1m)[0m && [1;35mraw.length[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m > [1;36m1[0m[1m)[0m [1m{[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                        raw = [1;35mraw.substring[0m[1m([0m[1;36m1[0m, [1;35mraw.length[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m - [1;36m1[0m[1m)[0m;                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    [1m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    if [1m([0m![1;35mraw.matches[0m[1m([0m[32m"[0m[32m[[0m[32mA-Za-z0-9_\\-./\\\\ [0m[32m][0m[32m+"[0m[1m)[0m[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                        throw new [1;35mTikaException[0m[1m([0m[32m"Invalid characters in command argument: "[0m + [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         arg[1m)[0m;                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    [1m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                [1m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            [1m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            ```                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. In the block around line [1;36m305[0m, the original:                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            ```java                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            process = [1;35mRuntime.getRuntime[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m[1;35m.exec[0m[1m([0mcmd[1m)[0m;                                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m            was replaced with:                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            ```java                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            try [1m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                [1;35mvalidateCommand[0m[1m([0mcmd[1m)[0m;                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            [1m}[0m catch [1m([0mTikaException te[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                [1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1m([0m[32m"Unsafe external command, skipping parser: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m, [1;35mte.getMessage[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m[1m)[0m;   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                return;                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            [1m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            process = new [1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1m([0mcmd[1m)[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    [1;35m.redirectErrorStream[0m[1m([0mfalse[1m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                    [1;35m.start[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m;                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            ```                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m. Removed the old `Runtime.exec` overload handling.                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Clean up and correctly place the `validateCommand` method**  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. In `ExternalParser.java`, locate the end of the `[0m[1;35mignoreStream[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` helper [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m139[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Immediately after its closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`, insert a blank line, then add[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe `validateCommand` JavaDoc and method signature—without any leading line-number [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprefixes or stray colons. For example:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    * Validates command array before execution to prevent OS command injection.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    * @param cmd the command and arguments[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    * @throws TikaException if validation fails[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static void [0m[1;35mvalidateCommand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m cmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws TikaException [0m[1;39m{[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       Path exePath = [0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mFiles.isRegularFile[0m[1;39m([0m[39mexePath[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m || ![0m[1;35mFiles.isExecutable[0m[1;39m([0m[39mexePath[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"External executable not found or not [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mexecutable: "[0m[39m + cmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mString arg : cmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           String raw = arg;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mraw.startsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"\""[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m[1;35mraw.endsWith[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"\""[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m && [0m[1;35mraw.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               raw = [0m[1;35mraw.substring[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m, [0m[1;35mraw.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m - [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mraw.matches[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"[0m[32m[[0m[32mA-Za-z0-9_\\-./\\\\ [0m[32m][0m[32m+"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid characters in command argument: "[0m[39m +[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marg[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. After closing this method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mensure there is exactly one `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m` closing the method[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mblock[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, insert a single blank line, then leave the existing `[0m[1;35mcheck[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` JavaDoc [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand method signature unchanged. This guarantees that `validateCommand` is a [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtop-level method inside the class and all braces are balanced.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Adjust imports**  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   At the top of `ExternalParser.java`—just after the existing `java.io.*` and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`java.util.*` imports but before the `org.slf4j.LoggerFactory` import—add:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.nio.file.Files;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.nio.file.Path;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   import java.nio.file.Paths;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   This ensures `[0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mFiles.isRegularFile[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mFiles.isExecutable[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` compile without errors.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Replace `Runtime.exec` in the `[0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method**  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In the `[0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaInputStream, XHTMLContentHandler, Metadata, [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTemporaryResources[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround the old lines [0m[1;36m305[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m316[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, remove the entire [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mblock:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Execute[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       Process process = null;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd.length == [0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               process = [0m[1;35mRuntime.getRuntime[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               process = [0m[1;35mRuntime.getRuntime[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.exec[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"problem with process exec"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   and replace it with:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Validate command array before execution to prevent injection[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mvalidateCommand[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaException te[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unsafe external command, skipping parser: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mte.getMessage[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Execute safely without shell interpretation[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       Process process;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           process = new [0m[1;35mProcessBuilder[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcmd[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[1;35m.redirectErrorStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfalse[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[1;35m.start[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m catch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIOException e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"problem starting external process"[0m[39m, e[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           return;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Ensure you keep the surrounding code that handles sending input, reading output [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstreams, and the final `finally` block that calls `[0m[1;35mprocess.waitFor[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` intact.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Verify brace balance and remove diff artifacts**  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Remove any stray prefixes such as `[0m[1;36m140[0m[39m:`, `[0m[1;36m142[0m[39m:` or other line-number [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39martifacts introduced by the patch.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Confirm every opening `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m` has a matching closing `[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`.  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure no methods are accidentally nested within each other.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Rationale and side-effect mitigation**  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By placing `validateCommand` at the class level, we avoid syntax errors that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marise from mis-placed braces or nested declarations.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The import adjustments guarantee the new sanitizer code compiles.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replacing all direct `Runtime.exec` calls in `[0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with a validated [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`ProcessBuilder` preserves existing behavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno shell interpolation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m while [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthwarting untrusted inputs.  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Since other modules and harnesses are untouched, existing tests and fuzzing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentry points remain valid.  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No broad exception swallowing is introduced—only `TikaException` and [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` are handled explicitly, so we do not mask unrelated errors.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Post-patch validation**  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run `mvn clean compile` for `tika-core` to confirm that the previous six [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merrors around lines [0m[1;36m143[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m144[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m164[0m[39m, and [0m[1;36m172[0m[39m are resolved.  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Execute existing unit tests for `ExternalParser` to verify no regressions.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re-run the jazzer harness to ensure the OS command injection sanitizer no [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlonger triggers while functionality is preserved.[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
